For the marketing year 2003/2004:
(a) the minimum price for unprocessed dried figs referred to in Article 6b of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 shall be EUR 878,86 per net tonne from the producer;
(b) the production aid for dried figs referred to in Article 6c of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 shall be EUR 264,83 per net tonne.
